full_text: UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE Form approved Immigration and Naturalization Service Budget Bureau No. 43-R423 AFFIDAVIT OF SUPPORT (Fill in with typewriter or print in block letters in ink) I, Olive BakeR . Residing at 284 Howland Ave (Name) (Street and number) Englewood (City) new (State) Jersey 07631 if in U.S.A. (ZIP Code, U.S.) (Country) being duly sworn depose and say: 1. I was born on Gug. $1943 st at Kingston Jamaica Also, answer either a, b or c, as appropriate (Date) (City) (Country) if you are not a native born United States citizen. (c) If an alien lawfully admitted to the United States for permanent residence, give 'A' number A17. . 2. That I am 27 years of age and have resided in the United States since 1967 . 3.
